---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact AGrowth" description="Contact AGrowth about a Meta, Google Ads, or TikTok Ads restriction, suspension, review, appeal, or preventive account operation.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container page-hero-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact AGrowth</p>
      <h1>Share the notice, affected asset, and recent changes.</h1>
      <p class="lede">For a current restriction or suspension, include the platform, affected account or asset, notice date, and steps already taken. For preventive work, describe the ownership, access, billing, or verification control you need to review. Never send passwords, full payment details, or recovery codes.</p>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <article class="contact-card">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="m5 7 7 6 7-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
          <h2>Verify the official profile</h2>
          <p>Use the GitHub profile connected to this website to verify AGrowth and its published projects.</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/agrowthagency" rel="me">AGrowth on GitHub →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="contact-card">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 4h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-7l-5 4v-4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"/><path d="M8 9h8M8 13h5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          <h2>Prepare the account brief</h2>
          <p>Include the platform, account type, exact notice, affected asset, timeline, recent changes, and available evidence.</p>
          <a href="/appeals-compliance/">Review appeal guidance →</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
